---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | CHINPK Packaging"
  description="CHINPK Packaging Privacy Policy - Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <div class="breadcrumb"><div class="container"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="separator">/</span><span class="current">Privacy Policy</span></div></div>

  <section class="page-header text-center"><div class="container"><h1>Privacy Policy</h1><p>Last updated: June 16, 2026</p></div></section>

  <section class="py-20"><div class="container max-w-4xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">CHINPK Packaging ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website www.chinpk.com.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">Personal Data</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">We may collect personally identifiable information when you:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2"><li>Submit an inquiry or contact form</li><li>Request a quote for our products</li><li>Subscribe to our newsletter</li><li>Communicate with us via email, phone, or WhatsApp</li></ul>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">This may include: name, email address, phone number, company name, and product requirements.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2"><li>Respond to your inquiries and provide quotes</li><li>Process and fulfill your orders</li><li>Improve our website and user experience</li><li>Send relevant product updates (with consent)</li></ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share with trusted service providers and logistics partners for order fulfillment.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">EEA residents have rights to access, rectification, erasure, restriction, portability, and objection. Contact <a href="mailto:sales@chinpk.com" class="hover:underline" style="color:var(--color-primary)">sales@chinpk.com</a> to exercise these rights.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
    <ul class="list-none text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li><i class="fas fa-envelope mr-2" style="color:var(--color-primary)"></i>Email: <a href="mailto:sales@chinpk.com" class="hover:underline" style="color:var(--color-primary)">sales@chinpk.com</a></li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-phone mr-2" style="color:var(--color-primary)"></i>Phone: <a href="tel:+8615939482575" class="hover:underline" style="color:var(--color-primary)">+86 159 3948 2575</a></li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt mr-2" style="color:var(--color-primary)"></i>Address: No. 88 Industrial Zone, Guangzhou, Guangdong, China</li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>
</BaseLayout>
